{
  "texts": [
    "As a video becomes longer, the computing burden increases.",
    "In addition, it is susceptible to manual parameter settings, such as artificially designed anchor designs and confidence values.",
    "Recently, a new query-based approach has attracted the attention of researchers.",
    "It benefits from DETR (Carion et al. 2020) in the transformer, using a series of object queries instead of anchoring as a candidate object and creating a new view of action detection.",
    "This method uses only a small number of queries, so the network has a simple pipeline."
  ]
}